{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00418/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00418"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:04:18"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman offers a man a basket of pastries."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00418","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00418"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1/f1785a92-b230-47b0-84d5-d3c2374a9e4e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:24:45.569Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When Johanna suggests that Reynolds may have told “someone else” that he doesn’t like “stodgy things” at breakfast, she insinuates that she is only one in a long chain of women (models, muses) whom he has worked through. This implication will be confirmed—but complicated—by Alma’s turn in his life.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:290.0219298245615,830.5811403508771,561.3596491228069,193.84868421052624"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1/d5b0602e-f38a-467b-9207-677fac1fdae0","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T15:25:06.065Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Johanna wears a dress in a similar shade of red to that of Alma’s <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW48871850 BCX0\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-01247.html\"><u>waitress outfit</u></a>, worn during her first meeting with Reynolds. However, hers is accented with black, the color of mourning, signifying the impending end of their relationship. The similarity in their clothing draws a parallel between their roles; Alma is, at least initially, just another woman in the line of girlfriends Reynolds has had and is ultimately disposable.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00418/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:580.9978070175439,460.5372807017544,618.9254385964914,351.6666666666665"}}}]}]}]}